name: Mackenzie Emerging Markets Equity Index ETF
longDescription: The ETF seeks to replicate, to the extent reasonably possible. The Fund before fees and expenses, the performance of the Solactive GBS Emerging Markets Large & Mid Cap Index, or any successor thereto. It invests primarily in equity securities in emerging markets.
